<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Reserved Book is Available!</title>
  <style>
    /* Basic styling */
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; }
    .header { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #0056b3; }
    .book-details { margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .book-title { font-weight: bold; }
    .footer { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #777; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">Your Reserved Book is Available!</div>
    <p>Dear {{userName}},</p>
    <p>Great news! The book you reserved is now available for pickup at the library.</p>
    
    <div class="book-details">
      <p><strong>Book Title:</strong> <span class="book-title">{{bookTitle}}</span></p>
    </div>

    <p>Please pick up your book within the next <strong>3 days</strong>. After that, your reservation will expire and the book will be made available to the next person in the queue.</p>
    
    <p>We look forward to seeing you!</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message from the School Library System.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 